int main() {
    int t;
    scanf("%d",&t);
    while (t--)
    {
        int n;
        scanf("%d",&n);
        int i,A[n],f=1;
        for (i=0;i<n;i++) scanf("%d",A+i);
        sort(A,A+n);
        for (i=0;i<n-1;i++)
        {
            if (A[i]==A[i+1])
            {
                f=0;
                break;
            }
        }
        if (f)

        else
        printf("NO\n");
}
